subject: Anyon else interested in Emacs support for junit
msgSnippet: I have written a simple emacs extension to create a test case class, add tests, and insert assertEquals/assertTrue.  If anyone else is interested, I ll write
messageBody:
I have written a simple emacs extension to create a test case class, add
tests, and insert assertEquals/assertTrue. If anyone else is interested,
I'll write some doco and make the code available. If not, I'll just do
enough doco for my own team.


Cheers,
